"       vimrc file.
"       My aim is to modularise the vimrc settings into separate files sorted
"       by its functionalities and store them in vim directory,
"       i.e. organise the settings in this file into separate setting files;
"       for instance:
"
"         - base.vim
"         - functions.vim
"         - mappings.vim
"         - plugins.vim
"         - etc
